Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:24.76,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H4FA6BB&\3c&H8F152E&\fade(300,0)\fs30}Happy New Year! {賀正}                                           \h
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.76,0:01:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We wish you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.50,0:01:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This year as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your continued support!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why Honmaru not bowing properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru! Do you ever consider others' feelings?{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember what you did to me on New Year's Eve, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.01,0:01:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,On New Year's Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.72,0:01:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot everything that happened last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:55.85,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)\c&H4435B9&\3c&HCAD4D3&}1992\NDaily rip-off-a-page calendar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A barber?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:01:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hair has grown quite long indeed, Honmaru. {not sure}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! After all, it's best to enter the New Year \Nwith a spruced up head!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.28,0:02:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Me spruced up too! {lit: will do crisp}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.03,0:02:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done cleaning your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.33,0:02:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shining clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I get it! You can go now, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you end up looking as manly as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:27.50,Sign,,0,0,100,,{\c&HCCD3D5&\fade(500,0)\blur3\bord1\3c&H76AAF1&\3a&H50&}Episode 69 \N{\fs45}The Best New Year Ever! {最高だぜお正月!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm excited visiting a barber for the first time! {h}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, come again next year! \NNext client, please take your seat.{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, you can go get a haircut first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mind? Thank you, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, that's impressive hair you got. \NHow would you like it cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Any cut is fine as long as it's spruced up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A bowl cut would do!{bowl cut; mushroom cut}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:03:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut-cut-cut-cut.{g} \NThe barber's is a funny guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks pretty good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Except it's hella weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! I'll take care of Honmaru's cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Next client, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be shy, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna do Honmaru's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:04:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need my head turned \Ninto a nightmare come true! {/mess}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.99,0:04:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Barber-san looking happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop the time and do it myself! \NIf I do it right, no one will notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's cut some hairu-ru-ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut some from the front too. Cut-cut. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Honmaru looking manly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.69,0:04:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've a gift for being a barber!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, where was it... {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Will do the back with the buzzer! {to taper (hair) at the back; to cut hair so that it gradually gets shorter at the back of the head}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, it slipped. {/mistake}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, looking like a nice road!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's build an intersection!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Will ride to the front too!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I played on Honmaru's head...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! When magic wears off, \Nit'll be lots of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? My scissors?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This...{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I do something like that \Nwithout even realizing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If the word gets out \Nthat I did such a thing to the client's head...{/if the world; society; people; the public learns ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! This kid's gonna hate it, \Nbut I'm gonna have to shave it all off! {close-cropped head; bald hill} {no clue what's before marubouzu, kinda hear kono kuni ha warui ha konomama ... but I don't seem to understand what it means; TLC}{6:20: I'm hearing "よし、この子には悪いが、このまま丸坊主"\NA loose TL would be something like "Alright! Sorry about this kid, but I'm gonna have to shave it all off!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you cutting more? \NThat cut is already top grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! What the hell is that cut?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone sees me with a haircut like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh! Weirdo cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, what is this hairstyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru is a weirdo in everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My life is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry! I don't know how this happened... {/before I knew it}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, why you don't like that look? \NIt's totally cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I see...{sateha} Taru, it was your work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry! Of course, I'll give you a refund...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it can't be helped now, \Nplease just make everything short.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what you wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, he let me off the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Honmaru! Looking cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right! Just super!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, I'll do something with magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This - Helpflute-kun. You can use it for various things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:07:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And the tune for growing hair is... Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good! It's coming out, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it! As expected of a great magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad! Honmaru is smiling again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It grew!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not Nobita, I'm Honmaru! \NAnd this is really not something to laugh at! {I hate this deadpun} {/not grew}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell do I suddenly have \Nthis excuse of a haircut?! {/funny/mocking head}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have a hand in this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone who hears this flute gets the same haircut!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, my magic wears off in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, just wear these earplugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Ten minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Gonna have to bear with it for ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, man! Taru's magic wears off in ten minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That flute seems interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play with more different hairstyles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Leave this to me, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru's magic wears off in ten minutes, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do now, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't show up in town with a head like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine! With a hairdo like that, \Nnobody would recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't make any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... How can I waltz in there and say hello \Nto Oaya-sensei and everyone like nothing happened? {hope he means this, in the sense "to think that I'll have to ..." tho unsure}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, I should try to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister Ria!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a hairdo that looks \Nlike the one you had before, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.58,0:10:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ke-Ke-Keruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Keruru, keruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Keruru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Keruru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Keruru is buddy of Niruru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It can transform into whatever hairstyle you want!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:11:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru's hairstyle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! With this, I won't be made \Ninto a laughing stock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to make do with this \Nuntil your hair grows back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Keruru and Niruru are very alike, \Nso if it sneezes, it'll go back to normal too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll be careful! \NKeruru, seems like we'll be stuck together for a while.{not this but the og is a polite-ism without meaning other than "we'll be together for long"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really delicious, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's the rice cake soup cooked by mom! \NIt's the best New Year's day ever! {soup containing rice cakes and vegetables (New Year's dish)​}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still some rice cakes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, can I have a refill?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for your turn!{/Don't panic - think he means this}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, wait just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Honmaru. \NSome New Year's cards arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What's in them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! This one is from Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a great New Year already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Honmaru? Read it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking care of me last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, girls don't like it \Nwhen you stare at them lewdly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's remain good friends forever. Iyona.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan doesn't think of me \Nas of anything more than a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Worst New Year ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose heart, Honmaru. \NIt'll get better one of these days. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In truth, we should've visited your place instead. {unsure, could be "we were supposed to call you"}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now, let's not say something so trite \Nfirst thing in the New Year. {TLC, assumed 正月から野暮な話はなし but no clue what he means}{13:13: I'm hearing "おいおい、正月から野暮な話はなしじゃ"\NA loose TL could be something like "Hey now, let's not talk about something so tasteless first thing in the New Year"}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa, happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Counting on you this year as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a nice way to greet an elder?{/say hello} {no clue what he means, tlc as well; assumed 良い挨拶ができるじゃないか but no clue what it means}{13:23: I'm hearing "よい挨拶ができるじゃないか"\NIn this context "挨拶" would mean something closer to "greeting" rather than "to acquaint".\NHe's commenting on how well they greet him.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like this year I got myself three grandchildren at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to be able to give you New Year gifts like that.{h}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? For me as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray! It's the best New Year already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Honmaru, look, ten pieces in mine! {/ten bank notes were inside}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! A whole stack in here! {stack of banknotes}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best New Year ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Sister got a lot too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I put enough in there. \NIf it's not enough, just let me know. {hope he means this, I wonder if it's too few}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear kids these days have a lot of expenses!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,An amount like that \Nis too much for the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Father. We build our upbringing \Non austerity and simpleness. {/out family's discipline is unaffected and sincere, with fortitude and vigor (vigour)​}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"Father?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Upbringing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to upbringing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you know about upbringing?! \NYou delinquent mongrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are to talk about upbringing?! {lit: are you the man to be talking about discipline}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll teach you some! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's New Year's Eve!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Matsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's tha'?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Congru-rutulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Congratulations. \NCounting on you this way as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, I'll feed myself to death with takoyaki! {unsure, assumed "I'll eat until I die [from overeating]" but could be "will eat takoyaki for the rest of my life"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That's quite some buck you got. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The New Year's gift I got from grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure you wanna spend it all at once? {not sure what he means: eenka ikinari tsukotte}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, that'd be a mistake to do. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that Tokyoites are used \Nto living paycheck to paycheck. {https://jisho.org/word/%E5%AE%B5%E8%B6%8A%E3%81%97%E3%81%AE%E9%8A%AD%E3%81%AF%E6%8C%81%E3%81%9F%E3%81%AA%E3%81%84}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't mind spending all the dough \Nthe same day they receive it. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But in Osaka, those who spend themselves to death \Nare called buffoons.{lit: spend so much they die}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You either invest it or save it. Thanks to that, I never \Nhave any trouble when Boss comes to collect his pay. {no clue, can't figure out what exactly is the nature of his monetary relationship with aniki there and whether or not someone has to "to have a terrible time; to have a hard time" or not}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Money is important stuff. \NYou gotta make the most of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Matsu-san is talking pure wisdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best New Year ever! \NSo I'll save my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, Matsu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna eat Matsu-san's takoyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Me love takoyaki! I'll make the most of my money \Nby getting Matsu-san's business goin'. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsu-san always kind to us, \Nso I won't regret it!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?{sayoka}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Much obliged, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, just admit it - you didn't really understand anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan is terrific in her long-sleeved kimono! \NThis is the best New Year ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Congra-ra-ratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept my congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised to come \Nto Oaya-sensei's house today, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is it that time already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But did you come all the way here just to pick me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What? New Year's card? But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... For some reason, \NI just ended up writing another one... {nc}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I sent out the previous one a long time ago.{okay, very long stretch but Imma assume she sent out the previous one that hon read in the morning before the confession, maybe even before he died}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:36.41,Sign,,0,0,0,,Please take care of me next year as well! {今年もよろしくお願いします}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end... Isn't it silly? \NI couldn't even find the words to write. {assuming she couldn't write something about love directly so the other side of the card is empty and this one says 今年もよろしくお願いします which is kinda more affectionate than what she wrote in previous card I suppose?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to hanging out \Nwith you this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is mutual, Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the best New Year ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, shall we go? \NI think everyone else gathered together already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, when everyone sees you in a long-sleeved kimono, \NI hope they don't swoon right away! {/faint from that beauty}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Long-sleeved...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, Taru? {no clue what's that ni in the middle}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? \NI donned a long-sleeved kimono too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks absolutely stunningly, Sister Ria!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Best New Year ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Honmaru! Ah, Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ria is not too far behind either...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations. Glad you could come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan is beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like champ and cheese, \Ncompared to someone here.{hope he means this, also no clue what's this champon but it's irrelevant to the message}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you meant to say {\i1}chalk{\i0} and cheese! {no clue if there's any underlying joke or not}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama, I wish you a Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And... Thank you very much \Nfor looking after me throughout the last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to your continued guidance \Nand support in the coming year as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And... In addition, everyone wished...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good health and...{no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora, I'd be happy to look after you again this year! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She actually practiced a lot for this! {meaning at ijigawa's house}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rival, I'm sure something good \Nwill happen to you this year. Don't lose hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Harako!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for a peaceful party. {/the noisy one came}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that... Neyo, how come?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's rare!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,See? That's why I didn't wanna come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Have no worries, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For Harako Tsutomu, #1 winner of the World Junior Street Corner Pick-Up Contest,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,hooking up with any girl is not a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that hooking up bullshit? \NYou just pulled me here by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You just can't stop lying! {hope its 一言多い}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, who was it that kept skulking around, \Ntoo embarrassed to come in?! {lit is "because it was difficult to get inside?" but I don't think neyo's that stupid}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised not to tell... {to expose (a secret); to disclose; to reveal; to lay bare; to let out; to give away​}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you be more honest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna fight?! {g, tlc} {18:56: I'm hearing "やるか、この！"\NA loose TL would be something like "You wanna fight?!" }
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice that you're so full of energy \Non New Year's Day. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how about everyone \Nsits down where there's empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I would've liked to say, \Nbut my place is rather cramped.{ sorry}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, how about we hold \Na badminton tournament outside? {hanetsuki (Japanese badminton); battledore and shuttlecock}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for the inconvenience. {no clue what she means by "I did consideration; concern; fear; worry; solicitude", either I was too considerate or I was inconsiderate}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this, Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.38,0:19:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't seem to understand your position yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, we'll have our faces \Npitch-black on the New Year,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,which is preposterous and unprecedented, \Nbecause ill weeds grow apace indeed! {(so marvelous or horrible that it may be) the first and probably the last​}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that clear to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, why am I getting the shaft alone? \NWorst New Year ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In badminton, much like in martial arts, \Nyou need to hit with all your might. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The men's team is nothing to worry about \Nas long as I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:20:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wearing long sleeves for badminton was a bad idea, \NI can barely move... Do your best, Rui-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I came in plain clothes, knowing that \Nsomething like this might happen! Right, Zakenja? {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my? I wonder who was it that made a giant stain \Non her long-sleeved kimono right before the new year?{actually also adds something about spilling something on it but I've no clue what's this asou she spilled}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You take that back!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so worried about my wig coming off, \NI can't move well at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best and cling tight to me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, paint me more! Pitch-black! Pith-pitch black!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Taru! That's when magic should come handy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'll do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I heard "magic!" That's unfair! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, isn't it fine? \NWe'll forgive them on the occasion of New Year! {approx}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The best New Year ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A sublime sight to start the New Year!{approx}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Good pigs happen when you wrist expect!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Good things, when you least expect."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nicely done, Taruruuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, go for another one, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's how they wanna play...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It tickles! {very much more like "tsurete" but only kusuguttai makes sense}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Honmaru, that's Butterfluster! {no clue, not anywhere in manga, assumed some pun around ドタバタ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.61,0:21:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes you laugh even more than Itch-Itchocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! We learned the lesson, make it stop now! {no clue what he means by "important; significant; serious; crucial is good too"}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But that looks fun to me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, not you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:22:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that haircut, Honmaru? Look at yourself!
