Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.94,0:22:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Honmaru-kun is weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.69,0:22:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Ikkyuu-san! {no clue what's this ikkyuu}{22:07: This is a direct reference to 一休さん an anime about a kid living in a monastery with a shaved head.\Nhttps://anidb.net/anime/1678}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did it come to this, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me, people! \NButterfluster, fly away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.07,0:22:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, everyone looks so happy! \NWhat's a better way to celebrate? {目出度い but no clue what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.05,0:22:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is the best New Year ever!
